                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 895.00/535.</note>
                        <head>[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-02-06"><hi rend="italic">February 6,
                                1911</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>The minister for foreign affairs has confirmed satisfactorily what he had
                            expressed in conversation concerning consular registration.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">O’Brien.</hi></signed></closer>
